## Adding a Title and Column Labels




::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
nhanes.samp %>%
  group_by(Gender) %>%
  summarise(
    n    = n(),
    mean = round(mean(BMI, na.rm = TRUE), 1),
    sd   = round(sd(BMI, na.rm = TRUE), 1)
  ) %>%
  gt() %>%
  tab_header(
    title    = "BMI by Sex",
    subtitle = "NHANES sample (n = 200)"
  ) %>%
  cols_label(
    Gender = "Sex",
    n      = "N",
    mean   = "Mean BMI",
    sd     = "SD"
  )
```
:::




